<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">据央视新闻</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">看完后</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">真的不禁感叹：</span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">能主持能采访能配音</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">颜值还这么能打！！</span></strong></p>
<p><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200923/5365483264f6438cb4c2ce626e459d53.png" /></p>
<p><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200923/6f7a2c71ba4a441daba79d8ab705a0c8.png" /></p>
